    <main>
      <section class="page-section text-center">
        <div class="relative w-full h-screen">
          <video autoplay muted loop id="video-background" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover">
            <source src="../videos/WebPageHeader.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <h1 class="section-heading text-uppercase text-color-e" id="oliveritas">FRESH ORGANIC EXTRA VIRGIN OLIVE OIL
        </h1>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-color-e">Single Origin</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-color-e">Grove to Table</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-color-e">Picual variety</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted">Imagine a liquid jewel, the color of deep emerald, hinting at the vibrant life force
          captured within. As it spills, thick and languid, it releases an untamed aroma – not shy, but boldly green,
          like crushed tomato leaves after a summer rain, tangled with wild herbs and the faintest whisper of fig wood.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted">Take a sip. Let it coat your tongue, a texture that's pure velvet, surprisingly smooth
          before it reveals its true nature. The first impression is intensely fruity, a burst of green olive energy,
          raw and vital.</p>
        <p class="text-muted">But then, it deepens. A provocative bitterness arrives, not harsh, but assertive, a
          confident challenge to your senses. It speaks of character, of sun-baked earth and ancient groves. Just as you
          embrace this complexity, a surprising warmth ignites at the back of your throat – a peppery fire, a tingling
          caress that blossoms and lingers, a passionate farewell that leaves you wanting more.</p>
        <p class="text-muted">This isn't a subtle whisper. It's the full-bodied, intense flavour of Andalusia itself,
          born from the passionate heart of two lovers, Jaén and Granada. It's complex, demanding, utterly captivating,
          and leaves a memory that clings, much like a forbidden kiss. It's the taste of intensity, inside a can.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section" id="product">
        <!-- <div class="container"> -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="model-container">
            <model-viewer src="../models/oliveritas.glb" alt="Oliveritas" poster="../images/main/oliveritas.svg"
              auto-rotate camera-controls interaction-prompt="Click and drag">
            </model-viewer>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl text-uppercase" href="">Pre-order</a>
            <br><br>
            <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted text-center">We really hope you enjoy it. For us, this is not a
              commodity, this is a piece of our land and all the sun it has received during the year. We hope you feel
              that warmth.</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- </div> -->
      </section>

      <section class="page-section text-center" id="project">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase text-color-e">TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF AND YOUR LOVED ONES</h2>
        <br><br>
        <a href="#product"><img class="img-fluid rounded-circle hover:rounded-full" src="../images/main/kitchen-h.png"
            alt="Kitchen" loading="lazy" /> </a>
        <p class="text-muted">We only get olive oil health benefits if what we buy is authentic. A lot of good people
          work for that to happen, but with the current model, it just takes a few bad actors to poison all the process.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted">The only way to know the true origin is with public transparency, and Oliveritas
          accomplishes that with Blockchain Traceability. A technology that can not be deceived.</p>
        <p class="text-muted">Our Single Origin Extra Virgin Olive Oil is also Organic. No poisons were used in the
          olive trees, and therefore in the olive oil. Organic shows we care about this planet, and our packaging
          reflects this commitment.</p>
        <p class="text-muted">We help preserve the social fabric by ethically sourcing too. The land is already to the
          tiller, we just need to maintain it and prevent vulture funds from taking over.</p>
        <a href="#product"><img src="../images/main/oliveritas.svg" alt="Oliveritas Logo" class="img-fluid"
            loading="lazy" /></a>

        <div class="container">
          <div class="text-center">
            <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted text-center">Click on the different images to see the sections of
              the project</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <% for (let i=1; i <=6; i++) { %>
