          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted text-center">We'd love to hear from you</h3>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl text-uppercase" href="mailto:oliveritas.oevoo@gmail.com">Contact Us</a>
          <br>
          <p class="text-muted text-center">Email us at oliveritas.oevoo@gmail.com to get in touch.</p>
          <br>
          <a href="#product"><img src="../images/main/oliveritas.svg" alt="Oliveritas Logo" class="img-fluid"
              loading="lazy" /></a>
